                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "**Four weeks after after birth, Suzie and Ma go to Jebs store. Suzie is confronted with hostility from Jeb the store owner, the community is faced with hostility from Cartel and from illegal crossing from Mexico into their ranches and farms (demonstrated by the new on the TV in the store. Suzie is approached by Aiden, an old beau from high school but Suzie tells herself he is there for Bee. \n"
